                  <div class="category_block_header">
                    <h2>
                      Diversity & Inclusion
                    </h2>
                  </div>
                  <p>
                    We offer a diverse range of games and gaming products that appeal to gamers of all ages, genders, races, and abilities. <br>
                    We provide a safe and welcoming environment for all customers, including those who may feel marginalized or excluded in other gaming spaces. <br>
                    We offer products and services which cater for every one of our client’s to  foster and ensure diversity and inclusion to  encourage minority – backgrounds communities, such as women gaming or LGBT+ gaming products and services.

                   </p>
                </div>
